=\"\" src=\"/uploads/attached/image/201505/dd9863a1404.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/attached/image/201505/b285d49f6f2.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/attached/image/201505/96cb3c6ac9d.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/attached/image/201505/3dce947d62f.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	360度环拥城市美景，享受怡人的茶香，品位纯正的甜品点心，丰富层进的口感，带来前所未有的满足。来一杯香浓咖啡或健康茶饮，并配以可口的水果糕点或其它甜品\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/attached/image/201505/1592f9031eb.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/attached/image/201505/fea78b69e3d.jpg\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	上海斯格威铂尔曼大酒店在上海市中心的卢湾区，毗邻繁华的徐家汇、日月光和新天地。俯瞰外滩万国建筑群，黄浦江两岸绚烂风景，世博园区、新落成的东方体育中心尽收眼底！\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;color:#444444;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:13px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:19px;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;color:white;background:#FFC000;\">下午茶菜单参考</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#444444;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:13px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;color:white;background:#E272E4;\">甜点</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;color:white;\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">焦糖布丁、巧克力布朗尼、酸奶柠檬慕斯、提拉米苏蛋糕、法式芝士蛋糕、黑森林蛋糕、日式千层焦糖蛋糕、草莓轻乳酪蛋糕、、日式千层抹茶蛋糕等</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#444444;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:13px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;color:white;background:#E272E4;\">Tapas</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;color:white;\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;background:white;\">鸡肉培根、玉米火腿、泰式蟹肉、蛋黄酱蟹肉、鱼番茄莎莎、鲑鱼慕斯泡芙、金枪鱼慕斯、牛油果鲜虾、酸奶虾仁、蛋黄酱蟹肉等</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#444444;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:13px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;color:white;background:#E272E4;\">卷类</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;color:white;\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;background:white;\">墨西哥鸡肉肠、墨西哥啤酒肠、越南鸡肉卷、越南蟹肉卷等</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p styl