\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5em;\">无论是双人小游怡情，还是家庭度假寻乐，这一程涵盖美食、雅饮、乐活、悦读、韵动、养生、静心的玩乐项目都足以让你全情融入到这逍遥的度假时光中享乐隐居。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"/uploads/attached/image/201505/1f5d1049ece.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><img src=\"/uploads/attached/image/201505/269df1da825.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;background-color:#00B050;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;color:white;\">扬州凤凰岛，绿色生态天然氧吧</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;color:#333333;\">隐居逸扬隔壁的凤凰岛，这里江河湖相连，水道纵横，大批白鹭野鸭栖息繁衍，是不可多得的天然生态氧吧；园内配有烧烤、露营、咖啡吧、越野车、跑马场、快艇、画舫等多种互动玩乐项目，俨然一处玩乐天堂。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<img src=\"/uploads/attached/image/201505/a3be48930e3.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-size:14px;line-height:28px;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#FFFFFF;background-color:#00B050;\">隐居温泉房、景观亲水别墅安享美梦</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font